{"tid":1536933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人幾時先明白，對家係想你越傷越好？","createTime":"2019-09-03T18:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T18:19:42.000Z","uid":97330,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"13dd00a167795fe7663a5f9abd85af1d1481a59f","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:05:28.000Z","msg":"我求下大家啦<br />\n呢幾日證明左，圍狗屋已經係比人破解晒<br />\n而且對家越黎越重手<br />\n根本同德軍集中營「猶太人死得越多越好」既諗法一樣<br />\n大家真係要放低多啲包袱同學精<br />\nHit and run係做完即閃，<br />\n老老實實<br />\n你諗下一個廢老都可以清晒成個連儂牆<br />\n即係話，兩個勇武去非狗屋既地方搞破壞都好足夠<br />\n前提係要做完即閃"},{"pid":"65b1cbe288307dbb7962d29bdd21913580bb7689","tid":1536933,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:05:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5a3e5a16b07237e6fe5c5b21d0389694d970c27","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:06:46.000Z","msg":"真係勇武，不妨組成小隊，大家各自搵target<br />\n咁先係真正既各有各做<br />\n<br />\n旺角輸左咁多次，心理學話會係同一個地方打，想羸返<br />\n但輸左係sunk cost，唔應該再記住"},{"pid":"118ed8780192573fa6f378973737afa06cbb2fa0","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:08:14.000Z","msg":"屌你樓上快撚到，勁揪<br />\n一個人洗足全日，都可以帶到風向<br />\n兩個勇武仲做唔到野？<br />\n最緊要係非狗屋快閃！<br />\n廢老一個都清到連儂牆，人多係直接打狗<br />\n但破壞根本唔洗咁多人<br />\n你諗下全港十八區都一齊有破壞，佢地去得邊到？"},{"pid":"903c50720386a5b4c8b704ad7075d3738be08bdd","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:08:26.000Z","msg":"自推x10 10/10"},{"pid":"8fde469fbf19f7c0be4760b2b3097a90c0084e5e","tid":1536933,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"難聽講句<br />\n<br />\n就係用和理非去掩飾美化自己既膽小懦弱"},{"pid":"1bddcccfec8de16a427fcc689a757a35f9334e6a","tid":1536933,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:10:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2947a350b5eafb6c852bba3ae5c12cd163b905ae","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fde469fbf19f7c0be4760b2b3097a90c0084e5e","tid":1536933,"uid":63757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:09:17.000Z","msg":"難聽講句<br />\n<br />\n就係用和理非去掩飾美化自己既膽小懦弱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:12:03.000Z","msg":"我都好細膽, 我跳閘跳完一次都唔係好夠膽<br />\n咁咪用其他方法<br />\n用廢老八達通<br />\n香港人太細膽,比人操控慣<br />\n快閃既勇武係唔會有代價架"},{"pid":"cf0d7c1173775d6ab092b548060c916ea462a325","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T18:13:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"44478a26fab082b9b8484899436ee920e1cb28b1","tid":1536933,"uid":97330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":